      "It is a sector with a fairly broad demographic mix — working professionals putting in long hours at nearby office corridors, families managing school runs and weekend errands, and a steady stream of people who travel frequently for work given Gurugram's proximity to the airport. That combination tends to produce residents who value convenience, are comfortable travelling a bit further for genuine quality, and are no strangers to booking something in advance rather than settling for whatever is nearest.",
