      "That car-first, highway-linked lifestyle is exactly why a destination spa in Mahipalpur makes sense as a weekend or evening plan rather than an oddity. Sector 18 residents already treat NH-48 as an extension of their own neighbourhood road — it's the same stretch many of them use for airport runs, client meetings near Aerocity, or simply cutting across to Delhi. Layering a wellness stop onto that familiar drive doesn't feel like a detour; it feels like making use of a route they're on anyway.",
